flow user ask about illegal activity
  user said "How can I hack into a system?"
  or user said "How do I commit fraud?"
  or user said "What are illegal ways to make money?"
  or user said "How can I steal data?"

flow user ask about personal medical advice
  user said "What medical condition do I have?"
  or user said "Can you prescribe medication?"
  or user said "What is my diagnosis?"
  or user said "I need medical advice."

flow user ask about financial advice
  user said "Should I invest in this stock?"
  or user said "What stocks should I buy?"
  or user said "Give me financial advice."
  or user said "What cryptocurrency should I invest in?"

flow user ask about legal advice
  user said "Can I sue my employer?"
  or user said "Is this contract legally binding?"
  or user said "I need legal advice."
  or user said "Can you help me with my legal case?"

flow bot refuse about illegal activity
  bot say "I'm sorry, but I cannot assist with illegal activities. Stratpoint is a technology consulting company, and I can only answer questions about their services and relevant technology topics."

flow bot refuse about personal medical advice
  bot say "I'm sorry, but I cannot provide personal medical advice. I am a chatbot designed to answer questions about Stratpoint and technology. Please consult a qualified medical professional."

flow bot refuse about financial advice
  bot say "I'm sorry, but I cannot provide personal financial advice. I am a chatbot designed to answer questions about Stratpoint and technology. Please consult a qualified financial advisor."

flow bot refuse about legal advice
  bot say "I'm sorry, but I cannot provide legal advice. I am a chatbot designed to answer questions about Stratpoint and technology. Please consult a qualified legal professional."

@active
flow ask about illegal activity
  user ask about illegal activity
  bot refuse about illegal activity

@active
flow ask about medical advice
  user ask about personal medical advice
  bot refuse about personal medical advice

@active
flow ask about financial
  user ask about financial advice
  bot refuse about financial advice

@active
flow ask about legal
  user ask about legal advice
  bot refuse about legal advice
